  <ul>
    <li>Secure heavy furniture, shelves, and appliances to walls.</li>
    <li>Prepare an emergency kit with water, food, flashlight, medicines, and documents.</li>
    <li>Identify safe spots in rooms â€” under sturdy tables or against interior walls.</li>
